This is an example blog post written in markdown. You can write your blog posts here and they'll automatically appear on your website!

![Drew Doughty](/post-images/test/doughty.jpg)

## Features

- Write posts in markdown
- Automatic parsing and rendering
- Easy to add new posts

## Getting Started

Just create a new `.md` file in the `src/posts` directory with frontmatter metadata:

```markdown
---
title: "Your Post Title"
date: "2026-02-16"
excerpt: "A brief description"
---

Your content here...
```

Happy blogging!
